resources.string: MyBatikFinder is an innovative application designed specifically for batik enthusiasts and lovers of Indonesian culture. This application makes it easy for users to quickly and accurately find and identify batik motifs. Equipped with the latest image detection technology, MyBatikFinder allows you to take pictures of batik and automatically recognize and provide detailed information about the motif. MyBatikFinder is a loyal companion for those who want to explore and delve into the richness of Indonesian cultural heritage through the art of batik.
